Class GLPrimitiveTessCallback

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GLUtessellatorCallback

    public class GLPrimitiveTessCallback
extends GLUtessellatorCallbackAdapter
    Callback class used in gl tesselation process. It is intended to create only ONE GLMesh with triangles in it, but it may depend on tesselation algorithm...
